The research methods knowledge base (3rd ed.). Cincinnati, OH:Atomic Dog. Gravetter, F., & Wallnau, L. (2014). Essentials of statistics for the behavioral sciences (8th ed.). Belmont, CA: Wadsworth. Field, A. (2000). Discovering statistics using spss for windows. London-Thousand Oaks- New Delhi: Sage publications. Field, A. (2009). Discovering statistics using SPSS. London: SAGE.
